Oakland.Skyline High School (Oakland, California:
Skyline High School (also known as SHS) is a public high school in Oakland, California, United States. It is part of the Oakland Unified School District.


== Administration and academics ==

For the 2014-2015 school year, the principal was Vinh Trinh and the assistant principals were Marisol Arkin, Anya Gurholdt, Elin Peinado and Christina Macalino.
